quest.title: The Lost Blade of Pacifica
quest.npcDialogue: Ah, traveler! I have heard tales of a powerful weapon, known as the Lost Blade of Pacifica, hidden somewhere in the City Center of Pacifica. Many have sought it, but none have succeeded. Are you brave enough to seek out this legendary weapon?
quest.objective: Journey to the City Center of Pacifica and search for clues that will lead you to the location of the Lost Blade. Be prepared to face fierce enemies guarding the weapon.
quest.reward: The Lost Blade of Pacifica is said to possess great power and will aid you in your future battles. In addition, I will reward you with a bag of gold coins for your bravery.
